channel.title: What is wrong with me?
channel.description:
[b][u]Bullshit[/u][/b] Every time I comment on something anymore it's complete bullshit with no thought put into it whatsoever. However, I did post constructively at one point in time (Or at least I like to think I did :P) and I must say, those times were a bit more enjoyable than today. I enjoyed helping others by posting useful tips/hints but it seems as if I have completely lost interest :(.
Does this mean it's my time to go? I don't want to turn into someone that everyone hates because I post random, off topic shit all of the time.
I would like to state that this is a serious thread. Thanks for any advice.
